# pandas-s3-reader-293194

AWS configuration utilities for Python applications.

## Installation

```bash
pip install pandas-s3-reader-293194
```

## Usage

```python
from pandas_s3_reader_293194 import get_config, get_client

# Get AWS configuration
config = get_config()

# Get S3 client
s3 = get_client('s3')
```
